_:N56e6b324f5a1435eab152732939af6f4 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Alan Mak was a Parliamentary Under Secretary of State jointly in the Department for Business and Trade and the Cabinet Office between 26 March 2024 and 5 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>He was Exchequer Secretary to the Treasury between 8 July 2022 and 8 September 2022.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously Government Whip (Lord Commissioner of HM Treasury) between 21 April 2021 to 8 July 2022.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
